snippet.title: Pikmin S Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Pikmin S is a Pikmin 2 mod created by ZachThePillow. in this all-new story mode mod, you travel with Louie and Davey across the planets around PNF-404. while exploring, you will discover new Pikmin, treasures, creatures and more on your quest to make money to help pay off Louie's ambitions to become a star in his own cooking show!

Discord server: https://discord.gg/NUWksAjFwz
